stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Idle
    Idle --> UserEntersCredentials: User inputs
    UserEntersCredentials --> ValidatingCredentials: Submit
    ValidatingCredentials --> CredentialsValid: Check validity
    
    CredentialsValid --> Authenticated: Yes
    CredentialsValid --> ErrorDisplayed: No
    
    Authenticated --> Redirecting: Valid
    Redirecting --> LoggedIn: Complete
    ErrorDisplayed --> Idle: Retry
    
    LoggedIn --> [*]
